{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778905248884,"sessionID":"ses_1d0fc1d88ffeOSTlNgkXE9cg8k","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"functions.read:0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/__issue_context__.json"},"output":"<path>/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"**Preferred term label:**\\nsixth lumbar dorsal root ganglion\\n\\n**Synonyms**\\n\\n1. L6 dorsal root ganglion;  \\n2.  sixth lumbar spinal ganglion \\n\\n**Definition (free text, please give PubMed ID)**\\n\\nThe group of nerve cell bodies located on the dorsal spinal roots within the vertebral column at the level of the sixth lumbar vertebra.\\nPMID:18316160\\n\\n**Parent term (use https://www.ebi.ac.uk/ols/ontologies/uberon)**\\n\\nlumbar dorsal root ganglion (UBERON:0002836)\\n\\n**Your nano-attribution (ORCID)**\\n\\nORCID:0000-0002-8037-076X\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd87Pcuyq\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"dosumis\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent  - please add this term.\\n\\n(I have checked the paper and the def, all looks good).\",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2025-11-03T13:02:48Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n16:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3618#issuecomment-3480415402\",\n17:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n18:     },\n19:     {\n20:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd87PdJYn\",\n21:       \"author\": {\n22:         \"login\": \"dosumis\"\n23:       },\n24:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n25:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please add this term.\",\n26:       \"createdAt\": \"2025-11-03T13:25:52Z\",\n27:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n28:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n29:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n30:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n31:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3618#issuecomment-3480524327\",\n32:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n33:     }\n34:   ],\n35:   \"title\": \"sixth lumbar dorsal root ganglion\",\n36:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3618\"\n37: }\n\n(End of file - total 37 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"**Preferred term label:**\\nsixth lumbar dorsal root ganglion\\n\\n**Synonyms**\\n\\n1. L6 dorsal root ganglion;  \\n2.  sixth lumbar spinal ganglion \\n\\n**Definition (free text, please give PubMed ID)**\\n\\nThe group of nerve cell bodies located on the dorsal spinal roots within the vertebral column at the level of the sixth lumbar vertebra.\\nPMID:18316160\\n\\n**Parent term (use https://www.ebi.ac.uk/ols/ontologies/uberon)**\\n\\nlumbar dorsal root ganglion (UBERON:0002836)\\n\\n**Your nano-attribution (ORCID)**\\n\\nORCID:0000-0002-8037-076X\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\n  \"comments\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd87Pcuyq\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"dosumis\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent  - please add this term.\\n\\n(I have checked the paper and the def, all looks good).\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2025-11-03T13:02:48Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3618#issuecomment-3480415402\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd87PdJYn\",","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"__issue_context__.json","time":{"start":1778905248858,"end":1778905248881}},"id":"prt_e2f03ef7f001XXlTtwuw3AUQCQ","sessionID":"ses_1d0fc1d88ffeOSTlNgkXE9cg8k","messageID":"msg_e2f03e390001KqV0GUeYYV8XMk